302
00:29:59,680 --> 00:30:00,840
Nichts.

303
00:30:01,760 --> 00:30:03,120
Absolut gar nichts.

304
00:30:04,920 --> 00:30:06,240
Eines Tages aber...

305
00:30:06,840 --> 00:30:08,400
